        "text": "Solomon came from the high places; having sacrificed there, so Vatablus; being put for  as R. Jonah observes (b); but the Targum agrees with us, he\"came to the high place which is in Gibeon, and from thence to Jerusalem;''and to the same purpose Kimchi; having been there, he came to Jerusalem: ",
        "children": []
